-- Greenhill CEO Bok Says Europe Merger Business Improving
-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 2012-06-07T21:17:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/greenhill-ceo-bok-says-europe-merger-business-improving.html
Greenhill & Co. (GHL)  Chief Executive
Officer Scott Bok said Europe has “hit bottom” and that the
firm is “seeing better results” in merger-and-acquisition
activity in the region.  Bok, who runs the advisory firm founded by Robert
Greenhill, commented today at a conference hosted by Sandler
O’Neill & Partners LP in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Laura Marcinek in New York at 
 lmarcinek3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scheer at   dscheer@bloomberg.net  